summary: A simple mod that replaces female facial dirt tintmasks with a trio of somewhat famous beauty marks.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://static2.nexusmods.com/110/mods/images/12989-1-1376532867.png[/img][/center]

[b]This is just a simple replacer mod for female face dirt tintmasks. There are three choices that I have recreated from some famous actresses and models. I copied Cindy Crawford\'s, Marilyn Monroe\'s and Amanda Blake\'s (Gunsmoke) beauty mark\'s from images I found on the web.

Note: I tried to get these beauty marks as close as possible to their original namesakes. They aren\'t perfect but they are near enough for me.

Installation: Simply download them using the NMM and go!

Mod Conflicts: This mod will conflict with any other mod that changes the female face dirt tintmask files.[/b]



[center][img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/12989-1-1376532397.png[/img][/center]
author: FalmerBane
